# Vercel API routes

## Hobby plan constraint

Max ~12 serverless functions. Add handlers to existing dispatchers:

- `api/admin/[action].ts` — tenant admin
- `api/platform/[action].ts` — platform ops
- `api/tenant/[action].ts` — org signup/settings
- `api/webhooks/[action].ts` — integrations

Do not create a new top-level `api/foo.ts` unless removing another function.

## Webhooks

- Require `X-Webhook-Secret` when `WEBHOOK_SECRET` env is set
- Allow `WEBHOOK_AUTH_DISABLED=1` in local dev only
- Never use stub `verifyWebhookSignature` that returns `true`

## includeFiles

Server code must live under `src/{server,types,utils}/` for Edge bundling (`vercel.json`).
